  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"height: 338px; width: 450px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t炎炎盛夏，让人不免会有情绪的波动，暴躁的坏脾气接踵而来，像个定时炸弹一样随时都会发生。那么，这个夏天，让我们一起努力，大声向情绪中暑说声：&ldquo;No!&quot;吧~~(*^__^*) 嘻嘻&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t1. Do you have a good temper or a bad temper?Cite some examples to share with us.</p>\n<p>\n\t2. What do you think about the effective ways to keep from emotional exhaustion(情绪中暑）?</p>\n<p>\n\t3. DIY one topic as you like, but remember to stick to the theme of it.O(&cap;_&cap;)O~</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tTo my mind, good temper and bad temper are compatible.There is no point of denying the existence of bad temper.It is how to control our temper that matters. If you ask me, the first thing we need to do is to keep calm before what happens to us. Calmness serves <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/magically\" target=\"_blank\">magically</a> to clear out the origin of bad temper in our mind.Moreover, flexibility is a vital ability we have to master. As is known to all that we're in a changeable world.The more flexible we are, the more likely we are to survive comfortably. Actually, changes are one of the reasons we may feel angry. As the facts are different from what we've planned before, we may feel worried and then Mr.Anger comes.As a result, there are a variety of methods that teach us to control our emotion.I'm convinced that everyone will make it, right？</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tBefore I reveal my own viewpoint, I would like to define &ldquo;bad temper&rdquo;. Everybody could be in a bad temper because of something maddening. But if someone get cross due to a mere trifle, then we should call him &ldquo;bad temper&rdquo;, or more accurately, &ldquo;<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/irritable\" target=\"_blank\">irritable</a>&rdquo;. There isn&rsquo;t an absolute justice in the world. Why shouldn&rsquo;t we make every effort to change the situation instead of being huffish about those injustices? Don't often get into a rage. This will not only offend others but also do harm to your own health. Face everything in a common attitude and you will find happiness is all around you!</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/795279/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543466/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543466\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544936/\">受够家庭琐事 全球首例机器人自杀？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544415/\">考前一个月英语四级六级新题型复习资料汇总</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544312/\">BBC看中国：“土豪”成英语热词</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544642/\">6大细节证明 你其实没那么聪明</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544970/\">愤怒女士辣酱！老干妈征服美国小伙伴</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544705/\">BEC考前名师专访:用好真题你就能过</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544644/\">再不做光棍了！手把手终极约会指南</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p544906/\">中国热词！“土豪”有望收录牛津词典</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p543637/\">今日免费公开课：把听说装进口语</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
